msgid "System Markdown Alternate"
msgstr ""

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: system-markdown-alternate.php
msgid "https://github.com/diecieventi/system-markdown-alternate"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
#: system-markdown-alternate.php
msgid ""
"Exposes a clean Markdown version of your posts (readable by LLMs, agents and "
"technical tools) by appending .md to the permalink."
msgstr ""
"Espone una versione Markdown pulita (leggibile da LLM, agenti e tool "
"tecnici) degli articoli del blog tramite URL con suffisso .md."

#. Author of the plugin
#: system-markdown-alternate.php
msgid "Diecieventi Digital Marketing"
msgstr ""

